    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Region of the upper atmosphere of the Earth containing a relatively high concentration of ozone, which absorbs much of the ultraviolet radiation reaching the earth from the sun.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
